headline: FICO Survey: 1 in 3 Indonesian Consumers Blame Banks for Scam Losses
summary: JAKARTA, Indonesia, April 08, 2025--A survey by global analytics software leader FICO reveals the significant risks Indonesian banks face as scams rise and consumer expectations shift.
